        "id": 1144624
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-04-24T19:04:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not going to (read: \"can\u0027t\") quote the C++ standard at you, but this seems a bit undefined-behavior-y.",
      "parentUuid": "7c326d29_e92804ca",
      "range": {
