      "writtenOn": "2018-04-24T19:15:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t particularly disagree. My only (weak) defense is that I actually copy-pasted this bit that was written by a known language-lawyer. :) https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/crashpad/crashpad/+/439644\n\nTo me it feels about the same as the \"struct hack\" so I thought it was probably OK. I can see how messy it gets to add and subtract 2 in a few places if you prefer though.\n\n(I should probably extract out this bit to share between _win and _socket, but it has some different types so it was a bit fussy.)",
